# Seed por API (opcional) - fiscal-service
# Base URL ejemplo: http://localhost:8087

### Crear serie BOLETA TEST
POST http://localhost:8087/fiscal/series
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "companyId": "11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111",
  "countryCode": "PE",
  "taxAuthorityCode": "SUNAT",
  "documentTypeCode": "03",
  "series": "B001",
  "environment": "TEST",
  "nextNumber": 1,
  "active": true,
  "validFrom": null,
  "validTo": null
}

### Crear serie FACTURA TEST
POST http://localhost:8087/fiscal/series
